Subject: drm/radeon: switch from 'pci_' to 'dma_' API
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: a5f61dd41273d75c63f226ab66d2e69dfe4dd045
